portpkg: Portpkg (Source package manager)
portpkg:
portpkg: This package includes the source package manager portpkg
portpkg: and additional tools. For more documentation see
portpkg: http://portpkg.berlios.de and /usr/doc/portpkg-*/.
portpkg:
portpkg: To initially setup portpkg run 'pp-config' and
portpkg: 'portpkg --sync'.
portpkg:
portpkg: FOR COMPILING SOFTWARE IN GENERAL, IT IS RECOMMENDED TO
portpkg: INSTALL SLACKWARE'S D/ SERIES AND L/GLIBC!
